00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,000
but I'll figure it out.

262
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,800
You're soaking wet.

263
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:20,500
Oh, come on, Lou.

264
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:23,100
