definitely trumps experience.

265
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:24,700
Does he have
all of his shots?

266
00:16:25,900 --> 00:16:28,400
Let me get you an application.

267
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:31,100
What the hell for?
It's a yes or no decision.

268
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,800
Not really. It's--

269
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:36,100
Hey, Lou, give her the job.
You're gonna give it to her anyway.

270
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:37,200
Zip it, Julie.

271
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,100
See, this is how it works--

272
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:41,400
