Would you like me here at 4:00?

281
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:03,400
Um...

282
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,000
Or how about lunch?

283
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,600
Then I can learn everything.
It'll be all good.

284
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:08,600
Uh...

285
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:10,600
Great. See you then.

286
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:15,600
Hey, that girl's trouble.

287
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:18,500
I think I just hired her.

288
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:22,100
( chattering, laughing )

289
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,900
Oh my God, you guys
are still awake?

290
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:27,900
You do realize
it's past 9:00, right?

291
00:17:27,900 --> 00:17:30,800
You realize
that you missed dinner?

292
00:17:30,700 --> 00:17:32,900
What happened to my dress?

293
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:35,300
Oh, I went swimming.

294
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:38,300
New York doesn't use that ocean
as a toilet, do they?

295
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:40,400
Is my hair starting
to turn green?

296
00:17:40,300 --> 00:17:43,300
Greta, I really don't mind
you wearing my dress.

297
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:46,600
