315
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:32,600
Karen: You know why.
We've discussed this.

316
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:35,000
I am trying
to save my marriage.

317
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:36,600
You would have better luck

318
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:39,400
