the polar ice caps, Mom.

319
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:43,700
Why is it that your marriage only works
when I'm not there?

320
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:46,700
Sweetie,

321
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:50,300
Greta, I know this is tough,
but try to make the best of it.

322
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:59,400
Take as much time
as you need, okay, Karen?

323
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:02,500
Sort things out,
shuffle them together,

324
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:04,400
do whatever the hell it is
you need to do

325
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:06,300
to try and save
this marriage, okay?

326
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:09,000
I'm here and I'm fine.
Don't even worry about me.

327
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:10,400
I'm fine!

