about petunias instead of money.

337
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:44,700
If Dad were alive,

338
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:47,000
he'd teach me
how to play the guitar.

339
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:50,600
If Dad were alive.
If Dad were alive.

