if you're feeling particularly sadistic.

375
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:52,600
Do you like shrimp?

376
00:21:52,500 --> 00:21:54,300
We have a spectacular
shrimp cocktail,

377
00:21:54,300 --> 00:21:57,500
