387
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:23,300
Welcome aboard, Greta.

388
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,900
Thanks.

389
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:27,900
Hey, that seafaring lingo
that you do--

390
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:30,100
you don't do that
all the time, right?

391
00:22:30,100 --> 00:22:33,200
Yeah, I want to see a collar
from now on.

392
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:35,500
This is a respectable place.

393
00:22:35,500 --> 00:22:37,700
Aye aye, Captain.

394
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:39,800
Oh my God.

395
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:45,300
Hey, you got a car?

396
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:49,300
