406
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:25,200
Does Lou know that you're
feeding his food to the strays?

407
00:23:25,100 --> 00:23:26,300
It's just garbage.

408
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:29,600
Lou know that you think
his food is garbage?

409
00:23:29,500 --> 00:23:31,700
No, I mean it's going
in the garbage.

410
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:33,800
It's just a joke.

411
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:34,900
Hold on.

412
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:38,800
My name's Julie.

413
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:42,500
I'm Greta,

414
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:46,000
which is just a thinly disguised
anagram for "great."

415
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:48,000
Okay.

416
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,800
You didn't thank me
for getting you hired.

417
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:52,200
That's 'cause I already
hate the job.

418
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:57,800
It's only been one day.

419
00:23:57,700 --> 00:24:00,000
( distant siren wailing )

420
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:32,300
( distant siren wailing )

421
