443
00:26:09,300 --> 00:26:11,900
Grams, don't worry.

444
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:15,300
They're trumped up charges.
Jury's got nothing on me.

445
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:17,400
What?

446
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:20,200
We found her over
in Asbury Park.

447
00:26:20,100 --> 00:26:22,200
She got a little scared,
so we brought her home.

448
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,200
Oh.

449
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,900
Oh, thank you.

450
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:37,700
( knocks on door )

451
00:26:42,700 --> 00:26:44,300
