from Asbury Park.

455
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:55,400
Well, you piqued
my curiosity, okay?

456
00:26:55,300 --> 00:26:57,600
Oh, I see.
It was all my fault.

457
00:26:57,600 --> 00:26:59,600
If you don't want me
to do something,

458
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:02,500
