in my head.

459
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:05,100
I'm just trying
to protect you.

460
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:06,700
It's a little late.

461
00:27:10,300 --> 00:27:12,800
I'm really tired, Grams.

462
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:16,000
