whatever it is you hooked.

490
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:28,500
Grams, I'm paying for this.

491
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,700
That's not the point.

492
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:32,700
You're gonna love this, okay?

493
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:34,300
I don't want cable.

494
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:37,000
Look, I'm almost done here,
so if you don't want this--

495
00:28:36,900 --> 00:28:40,800
