I just can't take it anymore.

499
00:28:50,300 --> 00:28:53,100
Oh, honey, so she wants
the cable TV.

500
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:55,000
What's the harm in that?

501
00:28:54,900 --> 00:28:58,300
Katherine: That's the point.
She does whatever she wants to do.

502
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:59,900
She has no boundaries.

503
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:02,700
Karen's always been
too permissive with her.

504
00:29:02,700 --> 00:29:05,000
Okay, that'll do it.

505
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,200
Finally.

506
00:29:06,100 --> 00:29:07,800
