1037
00:58:20,000 --> 00:58:21,800
Go on.

1038
00:58:21,800 --> 00:58:24,100
Oh, that girl--
she is totally out of control.

1039
00:58:24,000 --> 00:58:26,000
I mean, just once
she's got to learn

1040
00:58:26,000 --> 00:58:28,400
